<H3> <TI>   PRC To Train 60 Chashma Nuclear Plant Operators </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    PRC To Train 60 Chashma Nuclear Plant Operators </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK2604132894 Islamabad Radio Pakistan Network in English 
1100 GMT 26 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK2604132894 </F>
<F P=104>  Islamabad Radio Pakistan Network </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Sixty operators of the Chashma Nuclear Power Plant 
have been inducted into a Chinese training school for basic 
training in safety measures and maintenance of the plant. Under 
a contract signed by the two countries, the Chinese Nuclear 
Corporation is to provide various technical facilities to 
Pakistani technicians for the smooth operation of the 
300-megawatt plant. 

</TEXT>

