<F P=100> SYRIA </F>
<H3> <TI>   Assembly Speaker Receives Libyan Islamic Delegation </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Assembly Speaker Receives Libyan Islamic Delegation </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   JN2304203694 Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network in 
Arabic 1815 GMT 23 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN2304203694 </F>
<F P=104>  Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Damascus -- People's Assembly Speaker 'Abd-al-Qadir 
Qaddurah this evening received the delegation of the Islamic 
al-Da'wah Society in Libya led by Salim al-Makhadari. The 
meeting was attended by Humayyid Abu-Bakr Jallud, head of the 
