<F P=103> BK2804012794 </F>
<F P=104>  Islamabad PTV Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] In Islamabad, a Foreign Office spokesman has 
expressed concern over the report that India is once again 
inducting additional troops in occupied Kashmir. He said it is 
evident that while talking about dialogue, Indian authorities 
are intent to repress by force the legitimate struggle of 
Kashmiri people. 
  The spokesman expressed the hope that the Muslim ambassadors 
visiting Indian-held Kashmir would report an objective 
evaluation of the situation to their respective governments and 
