committed by the Serbs in Bosnia-Herzegovina. Nateq-Nuri 
expressed hope that the Bosnian Muslims who are resisting with 
empty hands against the armed-to-the-teeth aggressor Serbs will 
be victorious and will bring disgrace to the UN and to those who 
backed the aggressors. 

