<F P=103> TA2604162794 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem AL-QUDS </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] London, QUDS PRESS -- British sources have 
confirmed that Britain has agreed to construct a power station 
in the occupied territories as part of a $300 million trade 
deal. The sources said that the agreement was reached during 
recent talks in Tunis between British diplomats and PLO 
officials. The implementation of this agreement was "linked" to 
the attainment of self-rule authority by the Palestinians in 
Gaza and Jericho. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

