<H3> <TI>   PKK Fighters Cut Power in al-Jazirah </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    PKK Fighters Cut Power in al-Jazirah </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   JN2704170394 (Clandestine) Voice of Iraqi Kurdistan in 
Arabic 1530 GMT 27 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN2704170394 </F>
<F P=104>  (Clandestine) Voice of Iraqi Kurdistan </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] On the night of 24-25 April, an armed group 
belonging to the PKK [Kurdistan Workers Party] cut off 
electricity in Dahuk Governorate by destroying an electrical 
tower near the town of al-Jazirah. This is the second time PKK 
forces have cut off electric power in the area. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

