<H4>    'Arafat Arrives in Cairo </H4>

<F P=102> NC2804053894 Cairo MENA in Arabic 2335 GMT 27 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC2804053894 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Cairo, 27 Apr (MENA)--Palestinian President Yasir 
'Arafat arrived in Cairo tonight on a visit to discuss the 
latest developments in the Middle East peace process. 
  He was received at the airport by Assistant Foreign 
Ministers 
Badr Hammam and Husni al-'Ujayzi and the Fatah Movement 
representative in Cairo, Zuhdi al-Qidrah. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

