<H3> <TI>   Foreign Minister Receives Russian President's Envoy </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Foreign Minister Receives Russian President's Envoy </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   JN2604160694 Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network in 
