<F P=100> ISRAEL </F>
<H3> <TI>   Arabs Carrying Classified Information Seek Asylum </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Arabs Carrying Classified Information Seek Asylum </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   JN2804101394 Amman AKHBAR AL-USBU' in Arabic 28 Apr 94 p 20 </F>
<F P=103> JN2804101394 </F>
<F P=104>  Amman AKHBAR AL-USBU' </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Using the same northern point, 10 Arabs, in two 
batches, have managed to escape to Israel across the Jordanian 
border. All carried extremely important classified military 
information because most of them were high-ranking officers and 
experts. 
  The 10 agents have asked for political asylum in Israel. 

</TEXT>

