<H3> <TI>   `Terrorist' Shot, Curfew Imposed After Stabbing Bid </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    `Terrorist' Shot, Curfew Imposed After Stabbing Bid </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA2604061694 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 0600 GMT 26 
Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA2604061694 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>
<F P=105>  Hebrew </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] An Arab armed with a knife tried to stab a soldier 
at an IDF [Israel Defense Forces] roadblock in Policeman's 
Square in Hebron this morning. The soldier was not hurt. The 
terrorist was shot and apparently killed. Disturbances and 
stone-throwing incidents broke out after the event. Two Arabs 
arrived at al-Ahali Hospital with slight wounds sustained during 
the disturbances. The IDF imposed a curfew on the center of 
Hebron. 

</TEXT>

