<H4>    Economic, Trade Talks Held </H4>

<F P=102> JN2604170394 Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network in 
Arabic 1115 GMT 26 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN2604170394 </F>
<F P=104>  Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] A meeting of the Syrian-Russian group working for 
economic, trade, and technical cooperation was held at the 
Central Bank of Syria today. Economy and Foreign Trade Minister 
Dr. Muhammad al-'Imadi led the Syrian side to the meeting. Oleg 
