BFN 

  [Text] Cairo, April 28 (AFP) -- PLO leader Yasir 'Arafat 
and Israeli Prime Minister Yitzhaq Rabin will sign the 
Palestinian self-rule accord in Cairo next Wednesday, President 
Husni Mubarak announced here Thursday [28 April]. 
  Rabin and 'Arafat will meet on Tuesday to put the final 
touches to the agreement, Mubarak said. 

</TEXT>

