<H3> <TI>   Fatah Deportees Return Via Allenby Bridge </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Fatah Deportees Return Via Allenby Bridge </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA2704170994 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in English 1500 GMT 27 
Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA2704170994 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Eleven Palestinian deportees returned home via the 
Allenby Bridge from Jordan this afternoon. They are all members 
of the PLO's Fatah and were accompanied by 46 family members. 
Since the Israel-PLO peace accord signed in September, some 90 
deportees have been allowed to return. 

</TEXT>

